datasets.name: b6790011
queryLines:
WITH max_date AS (
    SELECT MAX(DataColeta) AS dt_max
    FROM gov_br_combustivel.silver_layer.fact_fuel
)

SELECT FF.*
FROM gov_br_combustivel.silver_layer.fact_fuel AS FF
CROSS JOIN max_date
WHERE FF.DataColeta >= add_months(dt_max, -12)

datasets.name: 698e05d9
queryLines:
SELECT 
    'Brasil' AS Pais,
    DL.RegiaoSigla,
    DL.EstadoSigla,
    DL.Municipio

FROM gov_br_combustivel.silver_layer.dim_localidade AS DL;
